For this purpose, the candidate must: 

   Analyse and collect all relevant business information from the Case Study for the implementation of the corresponding business solution; 
   Design Use Cases/User Stories diagrams and align them with the involved Profiles. 
   Create an Entity Relationship Diagram (ERD), serving as the foundation for the data model to be implemented; 
   Implement the Business Application using Microsoft Power Platform technology; 
   Develop a concise and contextualised technical report, a technical overview of the solution, unit testing, and technical details concerning the developed components. 

The final product will be capable of providing an intuitive/user friendly software for managers and employees of GreenPulse Systems, and, ultimately, improve the overall customer experience.

